Can Audience-Based Buying and Selling Work?

Growing numbers of Web buyers and sellers are beginning to
think about implementing audience-based advertising online.
And it wouldn't take too much to get it to work, either.
The question is, Should we?

http://clickz.com/article/cz.3975.html




