Dancing to the Tune of State Regulations

Wine and song may naturally go together, but Geerlings
&
Wade has to do a complicated song-and-dance routine
to
avoid being tripped up by state liquor regulations. The
wine distributor is quick on its feet, though, and carries
off its email campaigns gracefully and efficiently.

http://clickz.com/article/cz.3977.html




