I'm a Junkie

It started out innocently enough in a typical suburban
middle-class setting. Peter saw others doing it. He tried
it. And he was hooked. He made it part of his business. Now
it's a part of his life. It's too late to change now. Some
things, you just have to live with.

http://clickz.com/article/cz.3978.html




